COMMERCIAL REAL ESTATE JPMorgan Chase to Build New Midtown NYC Headquarters JPMorgan Chase & Co. plans to build a new 2.5 million square-foot headquarters at 270 Park Ave. in New York City, the first major project under a city rezoning plan designed to rejuvenate the building stock in one of its biggest job centers.
